data.description: This one won't last long! Sitting on an oversized corner lot in a well-established neighborhood, there is so much to love about this adorable 3 bedroom home! The large covered front porch invites you to sit and enjoy your beautiful surroundings before you walk through the front door. As you enter the home you will first see so much natural light in the large and open living space. The dining room is just off the living area and is big enough for an oversized dining table for all the family meals and holiday get togethers! Next is your kitchen and breakfast area. There is so much cabinet and counter space as well as all of the appliances are only around 2 years old! Off of the breakfast area is a huge space to use as a laundry room plus a storage area or a play area or whatever else you may need! The laundry room also has access to a lovely, private courtyard that is perfect for a morning cup of coffee or a space to sit around a firepit and check out the stars. Back inside just off of the dining room is the hallway that leads to all three bedrooms as well as the bathroom. In the hallway there is a built-in area for homework, mail, etc and a huge storage closet. All of the bedrooms are nice and big with good sized closets. Other than the bathroom and kitchen, the majority of the house has original hardwood floors. Outside you will find a 2 car attached garage with split entrances of this corner lot home. And finally, the huge backyard completes this gorgeous home with tall trees, an open patio and large underground shelter. Come see this one soon! Realtor is related to the seller.
